}, Open  ]],

Cell["\<\
That means that the bulbs are replaced on only 0.86% of the days.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.947907527794922*^9, 
  3.947907555296651*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"430a6040-8dc8-4cfb-8c36-\
b91259cc5bf9"],

Cell["\<\
(e) If X follows a Poisson distribution, then Y is exponentially distributed \
with \[Lambda]=1.73 days.

(f) The expectation of an exponentially distributed variable is E(Y)=1/\
\[Lambda]=1/1.73, that means:\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.947907596797213*^9, 3.947907620637876*^9}, {
  3.947907796008922*^9, 3.9479078649508247`*^9}, {3.947915042006098*^9, 
  3.947915076199048*^9}, {3.947915118738166*^9, 
  3.947915122153887*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"0b7518ed-1ac0-44de-95b8-\
456f84730943"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{"1.", "/", "1.73"}]], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.947915083484733*^9, 3.9479150863643837`*^9}},
 CellLabel->
  "In[570]:=",ExpressionUUID->"0fc6a1ec-4605-47af-9c20-744689283812"],

Cell[BoxData["0.5780346820809249`"], "Output",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.9479150866651907`*^9},
 CellLabel->
  "Out[570]=",ExpressionUUID->"7026db72-f88c-475f-ae9f-826f78a481bb"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell["\<\
That means, on average, it takes more than half a day until one of the bulbs \
gets fused.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.947915094409445*^9, 
  3.947915116565681*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"c2024662-a1e2-4379-b748-\
d4ae508d265e"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["\<\
4. A fishermen catches, on average, three fish in an hour. Let Y be a random \
variable denoting the number of fish caught in one hour and let X be the time \
interval between catching two fishes. We assume that X follows an exponential \
distribution.
(a) What is the distribution of Y ?
(b) Determine E(Y ) and E(X).
(c) Calculate P(Y = 5) and P(Y < 1).\
\>", "Subsubsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.947905807386298*^9, 3.947905867051806*^9}, 
   3.9479154478976707`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"1acf043d-be66-47c9-b235-\
52ba693d61cc"],

Cell["\<\
(a) The random variable Y is Poisson distributed.
(b) The fisherman catches, on average, 3 fish an hour. We can thus assume \
that the rate \[Lambda] is 3 and thus E(Y ) = \[Lambda] = 3. Similarly, E(X) \
= 1/\[Lambda]= 1/3, which means that it takes, on average, 20 min to catch \
another fish.
(c) To calculate P(Y=5):\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9479152454842377`*^9, 3.947915362258684*^9}, {
  3.980444938530218*^9, 
  3.980444940194147*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"b558e786-73bb-403c-9897-\
8c00386c151d"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{"N", "[", 
  RowBox[{"PDF", "[", 
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"PoissonDistribution", "[", "3", "]"}], ",", "5"}], "]"}], 
  "]"}]], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.947915373431078*^9, 3.947915393139551*^9}},
 CellLabel->
  "In[572]:=",ExpressionUUID->"c884c96f-6dc3-4664-98c3-b5a87919d268"],

Cell[BoxData["0.10081881344492448`"], "Output",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9479153865942383`*^9, 3.947915394014226*^9}},
 CellLabel->
  "Out[572]=",ExpressionUUID->"cd3b9154-9180-4ba5-b0aa-899e4ce0e627"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell["\<\
That means, the probability of catching 5 fish in one hour is approximately \
equal to 10%.
To calculate P(Y<1):\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.947915438946411*^9, 
  3.947915493185907*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"c573aa18-4036-48b5-bd97-\
b7fdf808cfb2"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{"N", "[", 
  RowBox[{"PDF", "[", 
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"PoissonDistribution", "[", "3", "]"}], ",", "0"}], "]"}], 
  "]"}]], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.947915373431078*^9, 3.947915393139551*^9}, {
  3.947915510875617*^9, 3.9479155111414557`*^9}},
 CellLabel->
  "In[573]:=",ExpressionUUID->"281d76d8-6717-4062-920b-2d820b94b0f0"],

Cell[BoxData["0.049787068367863944`"], "Output",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.947915512122463*^9},
 CellLabel->
  "Out[573]=",ExpressionUUID->"86ac9628-9bd7-45e4-964d-be7e76b41324"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell["\<\
That means, the probability of catching no fishes in one hour is \
approximately equal to 5%.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.947915517801359*^9, 
  3.947915540789315*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"5c6d4a67-00e3-4e16-90ab-\
b9b13552462a"]
}, Open  ]]
}, Open  ]]
